        <Parent_String>machine screws (fasteners) [300033570], screws by form [300079028], screws [300033568], fasteners [300036363], components by general context [300241581], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
